7.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2個月前開始自學<br />\n學左基本rules之後就上youtube睇下人地點捉<br />\n<br />\n暫時都未同人對弈過，主要都係同crazy stone玩9x9、解下死活問題、同用smart go睇譜<br />\nbtw，如果學定石有咩好既教材或者youtube video推薦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學定石可以睇呢個：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLku534PwIYW0iHumAM1cqFWU0atZj1LHU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLku534PwIYW0iHumAM1cqFWU0atZj1LHU&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=c5c59bd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLku534PwIYW0iHumAM1cqFWU0atZj1LHU</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪應該盡量背晒D定石?<br />\n<br />\n呢個page你覺得點?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.learngo.co.uk/Joseki.php?Sequence=4-4,6-3,3-6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.learngo.co.uk%2FJoseki.php%3FSequence%3D4-4%2C6-3%2C3-6&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=f4732a72\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.learngo.co.uk/Joseki.php?Sequence=4-4,6-3,3-6</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新手背太多定石冇用 因為你d對手9成9都唔會跟住定石黎捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學幾個短既星位+小目定石已經好夠<br />\n你個網拎黎做quick reference就ok 但學定石除左背之外 最緊要係要學埋點解呢個sequence會係定石同埋咩場合用 個網好似冇咩點解釋到呢d野"},{"pid":"ebd9fb67205485ce238c3e8ee17956222836b962","tid":21012,"uid":48846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T06:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n個online go幾好<br />\n啲人幾NICE<br />\n啱啱捉落識咗個紐西蘭fd子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我最鐘意佢有非即時對局<br />\n番工得閒都可以捉兩手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點運作架? 而家淨係同電腦捉, 就係怕同真人捉唔好意思拖咁耐.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n例如一開始每人有3日總時間<br />\n你每落一子就加1日落你總時間<br />\n每人個總時間最多可以加到7日<br />\n總之你喺你總時間用哂之前落子就唔會當你超時負<br />\n所以大把時間比你諗<br />\n但如果你對手捉得慢係可以捉幾個月先捉完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac4a34f73268c439e29de0c8162928fddc893d2","tid":21012,"uid":30940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:01:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2個月前開始自學<br />\n學左基本rules之後就上youtube睇下人地點捉<br />\n<br />\n暫時都未同人對弈過，主要都係同crazy stone玩9x9、解下死活問題、同用smart go睇譜<br />\nbtw，如果學定石有咩好既教材或者youtube video推薦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學定石可以睇呢個：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLku534PwIYW0iHumAM1cqFWU0atZj1LHU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLku534PwIYW0iHumAM1cqFWU0atZj1LHU&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=c5c59bd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLku534PwIYW0iHumAM1cqFWU0atZj1LHU</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪應該盡量背晒D定石?<br />\n<br />\n呢個page你覺得點?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.learngo.co.uk/Joseki.php?Sequence=4-4,6-3,3-6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.learngo.co.uk%2FJoseki.php%3FSequence%3D4-4%2C6-3%2C3-6&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=f4732a72\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.learngo.co.uk/Joseki.php?Sequence=4-4,6-3,3-6</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新手背太多定石冇用 因為你d對手9成9都唔會跟住定石黎捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學幾個短既星位+小目定石已經好夠<br />\n你個網拎黎做quick reference就ok 但學定石除左背之外 最緊要係要學埋點解呢個sequence會係定石同埋咩場合用 個網好似冇咩點解釋到呢d野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明白 THZ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會唔會有D網講解下幾時應該做長, 尖, 飛, 跳?<br />\n有時睇譜, 見到一個大跳, 真係唔明<br />\n有時開左4隻角, 做左小小定石, 之後就唔知下一步應該點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似一個盲既人去左一片空地咁"},{"pid":"4bd2e876db813403395497382d6687890d474846","tid":21012,"uid":52972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:36:05.000Z","msg":"開頭, 大家都係各有各霸, 好少會一開始就殺個你死我活, 就算有交鋒, 多數結果都係一個交換, 你霸呢邊, 佢霸個邊. <br />\n<br />\n而前人累積左一堆經驗, 咁樣一套走法就大家都無蝕低, 就叫佢做定石. 其實你只要有本事行步棋你覺得無蝕低既, 你可以唔跟定石.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多人覺得開左個頭之後唔知點行, 我自己覺得, 到行得十幾二十步之後, 基本上大既空位兩邊都霸晒, 就要開始搞人地地盤, 而最關鍵既係, 你要趁搞人地盤既時候, 乘機同時放子幫自己霸地盤. 高低手既分別, 就係高手搞你, 你掛住守, 搞完一輪之後, 你發覺原本係你既地盤仍然係你既, 但係佢就唔知點解多左塊地. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢D就係高手啦."}]}